Class OrderItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.aber.dcs.cs12420.aberpizza.data.OrderItem

  • public class OrderItem
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a link to a particular Item, which is an interface that should be implemented by the products in your design, and the number of the specified item. For example, an OrderItem might represent a pizza, with quantity 2.
